dc_description_s: This data layer represents trails for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Portage_Trails_2016.gdb. The features included in the geodatabase are 'GreenCircleTrail', 'StandingRocksParkTrails', 'SteinhaugenParkTrails', and 'TomorrowRiverStateTrail'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
